		        				We are a young company always looking for new and creative ideas to help you with our services in your everyday work.
		        			</p>
		        			<p><a href="#">Our Team</a></p>
	                    </div>
		        		<div class="col-md-4 offset-md-1 footer-contact wow fadeInDown">
		        			<h3>Contact</h3>
		                	<p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Bangalore, karnataka</p>
		                	<p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Phone: +91-9902202299</p>
		                	<p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: <a href="support@instacar.in">support@instacar.in</a></p>
	                    </div>
	                    <div class="col-md-4 footer-links wow fadeInUp">
	                    	<div class="row">
	                    		<div class="col">
	                    			<h3>Links</h3>
	                    		</div>
	                    	</div>
	                    	<div class="row">
	                    		<div class="col-md-6">
	                    			<p><a class="scroll-link" href="#top-content">Home</a></p>
	                    			<p><a href="#">Features</a></p>
	                    			<p><a href="#">How it works</a></p>
